<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 02:04:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Cantor SPAC 和 Adam Back DAT 之间的加密交易被推迟</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/crypto-deal-between-cantor-spac-and-adam-back-dat-gets-delayed</link><description>备受关注的关于坎托·菲茨杰拉德关联公司与亚当·巴克领导的数字资产财务公司之间合作的投票已被推迟。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/isCQTjUduxkE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 21:21:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/crypto-deal-between-cantor-spac-and-adam-back-dat-gets-delayed</guid></item><item><title>最大的加密货币买家望而却步，比特币再次跌破 60,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-breaks-60-000-again-as-crypto-s-biggest-buyers-wobble</link><description>比特币跌回 60,000 美元以下，重新引发了过去两年加密货币领域基本没有的担忧：当市场最大买家面临压力而散户交易者失去兴趣时，会发生什么。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJOvnMXh864o/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 18:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-breaks-60-000-again-as-crypto-s-biggest-buyers-wobble</guid></item><item><title>比特币撤退的零售大军暴露出新的脆弱性</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-s-retreating-retail-army-exposes-fresh-market-fragility</link><description>比特币多年来一直试图摆脱其作为投机散户交易者游乐场的声誉。它最近的抛售暴露了这种权衡：华尔街带来了规模和合法性，但曾经帮助吸收急剧下跌的散户买家基本上消失了。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDWGM9hBqFxc/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 12:27:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/bitcoin-s-retreating-retail-army-exposes-fresh-market-fragility</guid></item><item><title>塞勒面临比特币困境，没有简单的出路</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/saylor-s-best-bet-may-be-to-halt-strategy-s-bitcoin-btc-buying-spree</link><description>Michael Saylor 的比特币购买机器 Strategy Inc. 如果想恢复市场对其股票的信心，就应该停止购买这种加密货币。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCn0ThsHx9F0/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 07:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-24/saylor-s-best-bet-may-be-to-halt-strategy-s-bitcoin-btc-buying-spree</guid></item><item><title>马特·达蒙重返数字资产世界</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-23/matt-damon-takes-a-journey-back-to-the-digital-asset-world</link><description>越来越多的迹象表明加密货币可能正在形成底部。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iCKyBl.0AWt4/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-23/matt-damon-takes-a-journey-back-to-the-digital-asset-world</guid></item><item><title>科技股抛售引发避险情绪，比特币触及两周低点</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/bitcoin-hits-two-week-low-as-tech-selloff-sparks-risk-off-mood</link><description>由于科技股的抛售打击了风险资产，比特币跌至近两周低点。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iD6CSZF2Ssmo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 09:33:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/bitcoin-hits-two-week-low-as-tech-selloff-sparks-risk-off-mood</guid></item><item><title>与以太坊相关的非营利组织在“充满挑战的时代”削减了 40% 的预算</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/ether-linked-nonprofit-cuts-budget-40-during-challenging-era</link><description>帮助创建世界第二大加密货币以太币底层技术的程序员维塔利克·布特林 (Vitalik Buterin) 表示，其背后的非营利组织正被迫做出一些艰难的决定。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iqeD3m9kLhdQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 18:42:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/ether-linked-nonprofit-cuts-budget-40-during-challenging-era</guid></item><item><title>加密货币评论家 Nouriel Roubini 发现了区块链的用途</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/crypto-critic-nouriel-roubini-finds-a-use-for-the-blockchain</link><description>经济学家努里尔·鲁比尼 (Nouriel Roubini) 因预测 2008 年金融危机以及后来对加密货币的尖锐批评而闻名，他正在将他的一款投资产品放在区块链上。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ilit_FMYS38Q/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 13:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/crypto-critic-nouriel-roubini-finds-a-use-for-the-blockchain</guid></item><item><title>加纳创立的加密货币交易所在股权融资中着眼于外国人</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/ghanaian-founded-crypto-exchange-eyes-foreigners-in-equity-round</link><description>Hyro Exchange 是加纳第一家成立的加密货币交易所，在完成最近的种子融资后，正在考虑发行额外的股票，以加速在加纳和主要非洲市场的扩张。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i0Xn2y67F9Wc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jun 2026 10:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-23/ghanaian-founded-crypto-exchange-eyes-foreigners-in-equity-round</guid></item></channel></rss>